==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pight
<hw>Pight</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <mord>of
<er>Pitch</er>, to throw; -- used also adjectively</mord>. <def>Pitched;
fixed; determined.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>[His horse] <qex>pight</qex> him on the pommel of his head.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I found him <qex>pight</qex> to do it.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pightel</ent>⟦br⟧
